Big congratulations  to Juan Nunez on his promotion to Regional Vice President!! Juan reached out about 1 year & 3 months ago saying he was tired and ready to take business serious after being in for several months with no activity. He went to work, all while running his Resturant Businesses!!

Continue to build and support your team!! Next Stop EVP!! Let’s go!!
#business #growth #inspiration
